 *   Second point.
 * <br>Sub-element(s) supported (see @href CATIABoundary object): 
 * see @href CATIAVertex.  
 * @param iRatio 
 *   barycenter parameter  
 * @param iOrientation 
 *   To compute the barycenter of the segment [Pt1 - Pt2]  
